OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1781678874
OL,3,CStarmer announces new sanctions on
OL,4,CRussia as G7 leaders meet for talks in
OL,5,CFrance
OL,7,FThe UK has unveiled new sanctions that
OL,8,Faim to ramp up pressure on Russia as
OL,9,FSir Keir Starmer attends the G7 summit
OL,10,Fin France.
OL,12,FThe package of 70 new sanctions
OL,13,Ftargets Russia's shadow fleet,
OL,14,Fmilitary procurement supply chains and
OL,15,Fillicit finance networks used to avoid
OL,16,Fsanctions.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
