FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1781678874
OL,3,CStarmer announces new sanctions on
OL,4,CRussia as G7 leaders meet for talks in
OL,5,CFrance
OL,7,FThey target a front company called
OL,8,FNeptune, which the UK says is involved
OL,9,Fin procuring Western technology for
OL,10,FRussian military intelligence, as well
OL,11,Fas three companies and 10 officers
OL,12,Ffrom Russia's GRU military
OL,13,Fintelligence, suspected of acquiring
OL,14,Fthe technology.
OL,16,FThey will also sanction several
OL,17,Fvessels identified as moving banned
OL,18,FRussian liquefied natural gas and
OL,19,Fbring the number of sanctioned shadow
OL,20,Ffleet and Russian LNG vessels to more
OL,21,Fthan 600.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1781678874
OL,3,CStarmer announces new sanctions on
OL,4,CRussia as G7 leaders meet for talks in
OL,5,CFrance
OL,7,FThird-country suppliers helping Moscow
OL,8,Fmove money internationally will also
OL,9,Fbe targeted.
OL,11,FThe prime minister said: "Russia's
OL,12,Faggression threatens not just Ukraine,
OL,13,Fbut the security of all Europe.
OL,15,F"That is why the UK is stepping up `
OL,16,Fchoking off the revenues that fuel
OL,17,FPutin's war and powering Ukraine
OL,18,Fthrough the winters ahead.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
