PN,31704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1781678874
OL,3,CStarmer announces new sanctions on
OL,4,CRussia as G7 leaders meet for talks in
OL,5,CFrance
OL,7,F"We will stand with Ukraine for as
OL,8,Flong as it takes and this announcement
OL,9,Freinforces that. Putin should roll
OL,10,Fback his tanks, end his barbaric
OL,11,Fstrikes, and come to the negotiating
OL,12,Ftable."
OL,14,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,15,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,16,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,17,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
