PN,31705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1781678874
OL,3,CStarmer announces new sanctions on
OL,4,CRussia as G7 leaders meet for talks in
OL,5,CFrance
OL,7,FOver the weekend, British troops
OL,8,Fseized a Russian shadow fleet vessel
OL,9,Fin the Channel for the first time,
OL,10,Fwith the captain of the tanker, Ajay
OL,11,FPant, 38, being charged with
OL,12,Fcontravening sanctions.
OL,14,FStarmer said that the new sanctions
OL,15,Fwill "target the vessels, the money
OL,16,Fand the actors propping up Russia's
OL,17,Fwar economy".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
