FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1781678874
OL,3,CStarmer announces new sanctions on
OL,4,CRussia as G7 leaders meet for talks in
OL,5,CFrance
OL,7,FHe promised to work with G7 allies to
OL,8,Fincrease pressure on Russian President
OL,9,FVladimir Putin to bring peace back to
OL,10,FEurope.
OL,12,FIn addition to the sanctions, Starmer
OL,13,Fhas pledged that UK-based Urenco will
OL,14,Fhelp supply enriched uranium to
OL,15,FUkraine for nuclear power in a two-
OL,16,Fyear deal agreed last week with #210
OL,17,Fmillion of UK Export Finance support.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1781678874
OL,3,CStarmer announces new sanctions on
OL,4,CRussia as G7 leaders meet for talks in
OL,5,CFrance
OL,7,FAll of this comes at a time when
OL,8,FStarmer is facing mounting pressure
OL,9,Fover his military spending in the UK
OL,10,Ffollowing the resignation of his
OL,11,FDefence Secretary, John Healey over
OL,12,Fdefence funding.
OL,14,FAnd there is potential for friction
OL,15,Fwith US President Donald Trump, who
OL,16,Fwas pictured sitting next to Starmer
OL,17,Fat a working leaders' dinner on the
OL,18,Ffirst night of the summit, amid a
OL,19,Fstrained relationship.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
