PN,31708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1781678874
OL,3,CStarmer announces new sanctions on
OL,4,CRussia as G7 leaders meet for talks in
OL,5,CFrance
OL,7,FOn Monday morning, the PM announced a
OL,8,Fsocial media ban for under-16s after
OL,9,FTrump's pro-tech US administration
OL,10,Fwarned against such a move.
OL,12,FAnd recent interventions from US vice
OL,13,Fpresident JD Vance and US defence
OL,14,Fsecretary Pete Hegseth linked to the
OL,15,Fmurder of student Henry Nowak prompted
OL,16,FNo 10 to criticise those seeking to
OL,17,F"interfere in our democracy".
OL,26,@yD@AOUyD@\O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/11
