PN,31709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1781678874
OL,3,CStarmer announces new sanctions on
OL,4,CRussia as G7 leaders meet for talks in
OL,5,CFrance
OL,7,FThe Prime Minister and his wife, Lady
OL,8,FVictoria Starmer, met German
OL,9,FChancellor Friedrich Merz at the
OL,10,Fsummit on Monday.
OL,12,FAccording to a Downing Street
OL,13,Fspokesperson, Starmer updated Merz on
OL,14,Fhis social media ban, and they
OL,15,Fdiscussed the UK's ambitions to move
OL,16,Fcloser to the EU.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
