PN,31710
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1781678874
OL,3,CStarmer announces new sanctions on
OL,4,CRussia as G7 leaders meet for talks in
OL,5,CFrance
OL,7,FThe PM also met with Canadian Prime
OL,8,FMinister Mark Carney and spoke about
OL,9,Fstrengthening Euro-Atlantic security
OL,10,Fand innovative financing solutions for
OL,11,Fdefence.
OL,13,FCanada is spearheading the Defence,
OL,14,FSecurity and Resilience Bank, which
OL,15,Faims to help member countries fund
OL,16,Fdefence projects at low cost.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
