PN,31711
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1781678874
OL,3,CStarmer announces new sanctions on
OL,4,CRussia as G7 leaders meet for talks in
OL,5,CFrance
OL,7,FThe G7 summit also comes as Trump has
OL,8,Fclinched a peace deal with Iran, which
OL,9,Fhe says will see oil flow freely again
OL,10,Fthrough the Strait of Hormuz, the
OL,11,Fvital shipping route out of the
OL,12,FPersian Gulf.
OL,14,FThe US president said the strait would
OL,15,Fbe fully opened on Friday when the
OL,16,Fdeal is signed in Switzerland.
OL,18,FFrom Westminster to Washington DC -
OL,19,Four political experts are across all
OL,20,Fthe latest key talking points. Listen
OL,21,Fto the latest episode below...
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/11
